WEBVTT

02:08.749 --> 02:22.843
I’ve been desiring all the time that
I should go to Turkey or Tunisia

02:23.044 --> 02:28.161
where there could be an entry into
the Islamic world,

02:32.302 --> 02:42.477
because they have been promised that
they will be resurrected,

02:43.105 --> 02:47.231
and that resurrection has to take place.

02:47.432 --> 02:50.505
For that I have to venture

02:50.706 --> 02:56.166
and give them their resurrection which is
promised by Mohammed Sahib,

02:56.367 --> 03:02.125
I mean that’s My duty; and not only duty,
but I’m bound by it,

03:02.326 --> 03:07.258
that I have to tell them about their
resurrection and to save them.

03:07.440 --> 03:10.687
They deserve it, no doubt.

03:16.282 --> 03:19.904
When all the religions prospered

03:20.951 --> 03:25.009
in a very funny manner, I would say,
separately,

03:25.225 --> 03:27.905
everyone thinking they are the best,
the chosen ones,

03:28.106 --> 03:33.822
the highest ones, the greatest ones,
believing in themselves,

03:35.927 --> 03:40.107
they started going down and down and down.

03:40.949 --> 03:49.307
The reason is, you see, there is no respect
for each other.

03:52.047 --> 03:57.636
And the respect is not there because
there is no respect for oneself.

03:57.837 --> 04:01.209
If you respect yourself, you respect others
also.

04:01.410 --> 04:06.706
But when you have no respect for yourself,
you cannot respect others;

04:07.179 --> 04:09.173
but you should bombastically say that,

04:09.374 --> 04:12.998
“I’m this, I’m that, I’m that” –
any religion.

04:15.239 --> 04:17.889
Then your ego works,

04:18.090 --> 04:26.720
and ego makes you a person who does not
know about yourself.

04:26.921 --> 04:34.408
If somebody has respect for oneself,
he will never push forward,

04:34.609 --> 04:44.115
he will never try to be something
prominent, he’ll never try to show off.

04:44.316 --> 04:54.586
On the contrary such a person would be
hesitant to do something

04:54.787 --> 05:01.579
out of the way, something arbitrary,

05:01.780 --> 05:11.806
something showy, because it is absurd,
and it is stupid.

05:12.007 --> 05:19.171
So to do something stupid is a sign of ego,

05:19.372 --> 05:25.576
absolutely ego makes you stupid, and
ultimately with it you become idiotic.

05:28.377 --> 05:33.718
So the respect for oneself has to be
developed and as Sahaja Yogis

05:33.919 --> 05:41.357
you have to respect yourself: “We are
Sahaja Yogis, so how can we do like that?”

05:41.558 --> 05:45.707
As I told you that if you teach your
children all the time that,

05:45.908 --> 05:49.872
“You are Sahaja Yogis, you are something
exceptional”,

05:50.073 --> 05:54.232
then they will have respect for themselves,
self-respect.

05:54.433 --> 05:56.248
Is a very good word, “self-respect”,

05:56.449 --> 06:00.166
I don’t know how many people know about it.
Only when they are insulted or troubled

06:00.367 --> 06:03.623
they think of their self-respect, otherwise
they go amok

06:03.824 --> 06:08.852
and behave in such a manner that as if
they have no self-respect of any kind.

06:10.433 --> 06:14.977
So as Sahaja Yogis we have to have
self-respect.

06:15.178 --> 06:21.978
And when we have to have Sahaja Yoga
as our manifestation,

06:22.179 --> 06:31.160
as our personality, as Yogis, we have
to have a sense of self-respect.

06:31.361 --> 06:34.867
And even now you can find on the periphery
you find many people

06:35.068 --> 06:40.624
who lack self-respect and understanding.

06:41.547 --> 06:48.009
Some people are still sort of parasitic.

06:48.210 --> 06:53.254
Some people hang on to things when they
are told not to hang on,

06:53.455 --> 06:57.503
to take it easy, to work it out, they
try to assert,

06:57.704 --> 07:02.085
“No, we’ll be there, we are going to be
there, we are going to fight it out.”

07:02.294 --> 07:06.211
That’s not for a self-respecting person;

07:08.511 --> 07:11.575
it’s a foolish thing to do.

07:11.912 --> 07:18.270
Like two persons were going, one up
on the staircase, another coming down.

07:18.471 --> 07:23.543
So the one who was going up in his ego,
he says,

07:23.744 --> 07:27.787
“You better move; I don’t move for fools.”

07:27.988 --> 07:33.107
So the another one says, “I do”
and he moved.

07:36.406 --> 07:41.533
So this is what is the sign of a sensible,
wise, self-respecting person.

07:41.741 --> 07:49.044
He doesn’t go into fights, he doesn’t go
into unnecessary discussions

07:49.245 --> 07:57.307
and arguments and assertiveness, but
he sees – “Wait, is it worth it?”

07:57.508 --> 08:00.357
But when it comes to protection of truth,

08:00.558 --> 08:06.958
he stands up and he can find lot of courage
for the truth.

08:07.159 --> 08:10.404
I think self-respect is the first beginning
for Sahaja Yoga,

08:10.605 --> 08:15.066
is to develop self-respect in their inner
being

08:15.267 --> 08:20.119
as well as in their manifestation.

08:21.294 --> 08:25.586
It shows very well in protocol also,

08:25.787 --> 08:31.471
like I’ve seen people who - supposing
I have to go to Brighton,

08:31.672 --> 08:35.702
“Mother is going, all right, we’ll go
in Her car.”

08:37.954 --> 08:41.132
If it was for My love, that’s different;

08:41.333 --> 08:45.830
but just to save some money, “Let’s just
jump into the car”.

08:46.726 --> 08:50.023
That’s not a sign of a good Sahaja Yogi.

08:50.224 --> 08:55.171
Then it is also in power, when they have
to express their power, you see.

08:55.372 --> 08:57.889
Like the other day one girl came to Me,

08:58.090 --> 09:00.711
she had given realization, she was
all right.

09:00.912 --> 09:05.349
Second day she came, “Mother, I lost
my vibrations.”

09:05.550 --> 09:09.401
I said, “Why, what happened? With whom
were you talking?”

09:09.602 --> 09:12.140
So she told Me the name of a lady who
was asked

09:12.341 --> 09:19.756
to get out of Sahaja Yoga, Alice, and
she talked to Alice.

09:19.957 --> 09:22.071
This Alice was allowed to come
to the program

09:22.272 --> 09:24.900
but she took over as if she is a great
Sahaja Yogini

09:25.101 --> 09:28.698
explaining Sahaja Yoga to this lady and
finished her vibrations.

09:28.899 --> 09:34.863
Now this lady is such an important thing
because she was going to Florida.

09:37.052 --> 09:39.661
If she is just allowed to come in
the program she thinks

09:39.862 --> 09:42.163
she is now a very big Sahaja Yogini and
she can talk to anyone

09:42.364 --> 09:48.326
whatever she wants to, and spoil
the vibrations of another person.

09:48.527 --> 09:52.636
If I’ve appointed somebody as a leader,
it is not on the basis of their looks

09:52.837 --> 09:58.834
or education or anything, but on their
vibrations and their dedication.

10:01.177 --> 10:05.357
So the Sahaja Yogis have to seriously think
about it.

10:05.558 --> 10:08.485
Such people are always around to show off
their knowledge.

10:08.686 --> 10:12.884
You see, in Sahaja Yoga is so easy,
the knowledge part of it, it’s very easy.

10:13.085 --> 10:18.155
Anybody who is intelligent enough can read:
this is the chakras, this is this,

10:18.356 --> 10:26.322
they can give big lectures, explain this
deity sits on this chakra. It’s so simple.

10:29.727 --> 10:39.294
But the compassion and knowledge,
hand in hand, makes a Sahaja Yogi.

10:39.495 --> 10:43.966
Now some people have another style,
is of compassion.

10:44.167 --> 10:46.653
Naturally compassion is always sympathy,
as I told you,

10:46.854 --> 10:53.065
except when it is with knowledge is
all right.

10:53.266 --> 10:56.449
But just compassion -

10:56.989 --> 11:02.097
with compassion they will always sympathize
with all the bhootish people.

11:02.298 --> 11:06.413
If there’s one bhootish person in Sahaja
Yoga, he’ll bring ten more on Me,

11:06.614 --> 11:12.248
“Mother, look after this person, look after
this person, look after that person.”

11:12.449 --> 11:16.022
Firstly because that person was damaged

11:16.223 --> 11:22.023
and secondly because that damaged
personality thinks that,

11:22.224 --> 11:25.829
“Another is damaged, let us save this
damaged person.”

11:26.030 --> 11:30.073
All right, if it is so, first of all you
should be all right,

11:30.274 --> 11:35.342
and tell that person to “work on yourself”,
because if you try to help that person,

11:35.543 --> 11:39.621
your negativity will increase. You’ll go
from bad to worse.

11:39.822 --> 11:47.843
Always sympathies will go to a person
who is not all right, we should say.

11:48.044 --> 11:51.537
So you tell such a person, “All right,
you work it out this way,

11:51.738 --> 11:55.378
but I have nothing to do with you”,
or send that person

11:55.579 --> 12:00.215
to somebody who is an egoistical,
so they share better.

12:00.416 --> 12:04.403
There’s complimentary between the two,
and it works out better

12:04.604 --> 12:09.079
and saves Me a little worry.

12:10.342 --> 12:14.667
But beyond all this the combination
of these two

12:14.868 --> 12:18.813
actually must emit vibrations.

12:19.553 --> 12:26.297
It is how many vibrations you have within
yourself is the point which one should see.

12:27.656 --> 12:30.982
First the vibrations when they are,

12:31.183 --> 12:36.070
how are we to know we are all right
as far as vibrations are concerned?

12:36.271 --> 12:46.057
What is the sign of being a good Sahaja
Yogi, or we are really Sahaja Yogi,

12:46.258 --> 12:52.413
is that we develop a kind of a detachment.

12:55.668 --> 13:00.667
First the detachment comes naturally
because you are away from your body,

13:00.868 --> 13:06.771
so you are not bothered about your body,
you don’t think about it.

13:06.972 --> 13:10.115
That doesn’t mean you do not look after it.

13:10.316 --> 13:14.574
It doesn’t mean that you don’t have
any sense of how you look

13:14.775 --> 13:19.799
and how you move about, because you
have to be decently dressed also.

13:20.000 --> 13:24.600
But attachment means that all the time
thinking,

13:24.801 --> 13:27.482
“This chakra is catching, that chakra
is catching,

13:27.683 --> 13:33.321
my head is catching, my Agnya is catching,
this is happening.”

13:33.585 --> 13:39.764
This is the subtler way how Sahaja Yoga
can ruin you, is this all the time thinking,

13:39.965 --> 13:44.031
“This is wrong, this is wrong”, condemning
yourself.

13:44.232 --> 13:46.447
So this detachment has to be there about
yourself,

13:46.648 --> 13:50.706
“No, doesn’t matter, so what, I’m like
a barometer.

13:50.907 --> 13:53.518
If I go near somebody and if I catch
well and good, you see,

13:53.719 --> 13:56.272
I’m just helping that person, well
and good.”

13:56.473 --> 14:01.470
Or you give yourself a bandhan and just
approach somebody.

14:01.671 --> 14:06.736
So worrying too much about your chakras
is not a very good thing

14:06.937 --> 14:12.595
for the progress of Sahaja Yoga. On the
contrary, you should try to meditate,

14:12.796 --> 14:17.988
don’t think of individual chakras, just
meditate with your heart.

14:18.189 --> 14:25.110
So now you will see from My lecture,
or whatever you call this,

14:25.311 --> 14:32.374
is that you have to have a heart which
is open to Sahaja Yoga.

14:32.575 --> 14:37.364
When your heart is open, first of all
you forgive yourself

14:37.565 --> 14:41.553
and you forgive others, and you don’t see
to your individual chakras

14:41.754 --> 14:46.965
or bother about others, in the way that
you are concerned

14:47.166 --> 14:53.004
about one individual, but you look
at the whole as a whole.

14:53.205 --> 14:57.848
You will then start talking about Sahaja
Yoga – “How is Sahaja Yoga spreading,

14:58.049 --> 15:01.104
how many people are getting realization,

15:01.305 --> 15:05.269
how much responsibility I have done,
I should”.

15:05.470 --> 15:07.914
“I have done” means not ego out of it, but,

15:08.131 --> 15:12.990
“I should do? What work can I do here?

15:14.016 --> 15:19.553
What mistakes we Sahaja Yogis have
committed that it has not worked out?

15:19.754 --> 15:25.050
What is the situation? How I can help?”.

15:25.251 --> 15:27.918
This kind of a, you see, sort of as if,

15:28.119 --> 15:31.774
like you really become a light and you
want to give light.

15:31.975 --> 15:34.379
So what’s wrong with the lamp which
is not giving light?

15:34.580 --> 15:42.649
But you don’t think about yourself, you
think as a body, the whole thing.

15:43.031 --> 15:49.093
This is the first thing is to open
your heart.

15:49.905 --> 15:58.887
As soon as you open your heart you will
widen yourself, you’ll grow.

15:59.507 --> 16:08.079
For that you need not condemn yourself but
opening your heart is – look at this ocean,

16:08.446 --> 16:14.202
how it is touching all the shores but it is
in itself, in its own maryadas.

16:14.403 --> 16:18.495
If you try to press the ocean from any side
it will show on the other side.

16:18.696 --> 16:23.034
You cannot press it. It has its height,
it has its limitations,

16:23.235 --> 16:26.244
it stays in its own limitations.

16:26.445 --> 16:30.515
So open-hearted person is like this,
it touches every shore

16:30.716 --> 16:34.446
but keeps to itself, to its own maryadas.

16:34.647 --> 16:39.683
So this understanding if it comes,
the expansion also is in such a manner

16:39.884 --> 16:43.524
that you do not go into individual corners
and individual places,

16:43.725 --> 16:49.460
but you keep to yourself and you touch
everyone.

16:53.901 --> 16:56.881
This is the opening of the heart when
we say.

16:57.082 --> 17:03.289
Then a Sahaja Yogi will have automatically
a proper discretion,

17:03.490 --> 17:11.591
discretion how far to say, how far not
to say, how far to go, how far to behave.

17:11.792 --> 17:15.097
Immediately you can find out a Sahaja Yogi
who tries to show off

17:15.298 --> 17:19.459
and wants to talk about something they
don’t know

17:19.660 --> 17:26.481
and gets hold of ten people around you
and talk about Sahaja Yoga.

17:27.952 --> 17:32.402
Anybody who sits round like that, never go
near that person.

17:35.450 --> 17:41.077
I discovered a horrible woman in England
who used to do that.

17:41.278 --> 17:48.260
And then she formed a group against
the whole system,

17:48.461 --> 17:58.032
but she caught hold of the leader itself and
all of them had to get out of Sahaja Yoga.

18:00.947 --> 18:07.816
So one has to understand that we have
to be simple people,

18:08.017 --> 18:13.522
not complicated. For that heart has to be
open –

18:13.723 --> 18:17.402
that’s all I can say, open your heart.

18:17.815 --> 18:22.070
Not, it’s not imaginary, it is a state
I think,

18:22.271 --> 18:31.139
in which you have to be stationed to be
self-satisfied.

18:31.776 --> 18:36.437
This is a very good way of approaching
Sahaja Yoga

18:36.638 --> 18:40.409
for yourself and for others.

18:42.568 --> 18:47.257
If you want Me to say – rather
embarrassing –

18:47.458 --> 18:51.215
but if you put Me in your heart, heart has
to increase

18:51.416 --> 18:57.196
because of My size, you see.
You can’t help it.

19:00.727 --> 19:03.403
It has to grow.

19:04.111 --> 19:07.176
So that’s the best, easiest way to do it,
you see?

19:07.377 --> 19:11.061
You are such lucky Sahaja Yogis that
I’m there with you.

19:11.262 --> 19:13.770
You don’t have to do anything. Put Me
in your heart, finished.

19:13.971 --> 19:17.893
You are all right now, no problem.

19:21.149 --> 19:27.249
Not that “I love you, Mother”, but is
the point is,

19:27.450 --> 19:30.847
“I put you in my heart.”

19:31.683 --> 19:40.936
But don’t ever think like this: “Mother
loves me, because I can cook for Mother,

19:41.137 --> 19:46.048
because I can look after Her sari, I can
press Her sari” - then it’s ego.

19:46.249 --> 19:48.775
The other way round becomes immediately
ego, I tell you.

19:48.976 --> 19:56.775
I didn’t know but there are instances of
this kind. Immediately it becomes an ego.

19:57.535 --> 20:02.188
But if you say, “How much I love Mother” -
just admire yourself -

20:02.389 --> 20:06.361
“Oh, I love Mother so much.”

20:06.570 --> 20:15.117
And you’ll feel very fine within your
heart, as so joy-giving.

20:15.483 --> 20:22.587
Imagine people who never had Me with them,
who came on this earth,

20:22.788 --> 20:27.006
had to fight for dharma, had to fight
for righteousness

20:27.207 --> 20:31.216
and for truth, how they must have fought.

20:31.417 --> 20:38.534
But I am before you, so it is, “How much
I love my Mother”.

20:40.115 --> 20:47.090
Is a very simple method, a basic method
for every Sahaja Yogi

20:47.291 --> 20:51.561
to discover oneself, and to develop
oneself.

20:58.150 --> 21:08.707
Then the discretion, the light, everything
just starts emitting.

21:08.908 --> 21:14.748
You see yourself in that light and you walk
in that light

21:15.691 --> 21:19.679
and people see that you have light.

21:23.308 --> 21:27.474
Now you are convinced about Me. You have
seen

21:27.675 --> 21:32.517
photographs, you have seen the sun,
the reaction, everything you have seen it.

21:32.718 --> 21:38.898
So now that you can love such a person,

21:39.686 --> 21:50.994
itself is a very big boon for us that we
love Mother.

21:52.696 --> 21:57.722
Even if you think that I have not yet said
“hello” to you,

21:57.923 --> 22:02.377
or sometimes I may not look at you – maybe.

22:03.601 --> 22:07.145
But it’s not Me – it’s you.

22:07.346 --> 22:11.562
I, in any case, love the whole world –
is no question!

22:11.984 --> 22:14.766
Nobody more, nobody less.

22:14.967 --> 22:18.539
But how far you are closer to Me depends
on you, you see,

22:18.740 --> 22:26.625
because I’m a fixed quantity. How far you
move towards Me is the point.

22:26.992 --> 22:30.119
I’m a fixed quantity and sometimes people
are amazed that,

22:30.320 --> 22:36.008
“Why Mother was not all right with us
this time?”

22:36.209 --> 22:42.421
Actually, I stand wherever I am, but you
have moved away.

22:42.622 --> 22:47.432
So all kinds of discretions start flowing
into you.

22:51.133 --> 22:56.434
Even you are convinced that I’m
the Adi Shakti

22:56.635 --> 23:03.597
and there are so many convincing facts
that you have – photographs are there,

23:03.798 --> 23:09.481
and all happenings are there, miracles,
everything, everything is there -

23:11.745 --> 23:18.268
still you are floating, floating on these
ideas

23:20.563 --> 23:26.577
that, “Oh, look at this, this is Mother’s
photograph, this is what has happened.”

23:26.778 --> 23:29.365
Still you are floating.

23:32.383 --> 23:36.453
If you really want to go deep down,

23:37.883 --> 23:41.783
you have to just feel your heart.

23:43.015 --> 23:46.035
There you’ll find the miracle.

23:46.236 --> 23:50.562
These outside miracles are to push you in

23:50.763 --> 23:55.646
and there you will grow, and grow in
a better way.

23:55.847 --> 24:01.758
That’s the only thing we have to find out
and discover.

24:01.959 --> 24:05.326
This will really help Sahaja Yogis who are
new, you see,

24:05.527 --> 24:10.218
when they will see how you love Mother.

24:11.275 --> 24:17.296
Yesterday only we had parked our car
in a funny way perhaps, maybe,

24:17.497 --> 24:22.700
and they were all about to quarrel
and fight Mr Guido.

24:22.901 --> 24:25.443
They might have beaten him, beaten him
also,

24:25.644 --> 24:27.007
but he said - “Why did you park here?”

24:27.208 --> 24:29.303
He said, “It’s my Mother who has come,
I’ve parked it here

24:29.504 --> 24:33.511
because my Mother can’t do this”, finished.

24:33.792 --> 24:40.813
As it is anybody who loves his mother, as
it is, is regarded something very good.

24:41.681 --> 24:44.510
Now the mother is horrid;

24:44.711 --> 24:49.188
still if you tell them, “My mother is
horrid”, people won’t like it.

24:49.389 --> 24:54.949
But you say that, “I love Adi Shakti.”

