[Shri Mataji: Who is it?
Yogi: Oh. Put him out.

25:02.642 --> 25:05.418
Shri Mataji: Who is he?
Yogi 2: What does he?

25:05.619 --> 25:07.232
Yogi: Mr Mauro (?) from Switzerland,
Shri Mataji.

25:07.433 --> 25:09.770
Shri Mataji: Eh?
Yogi: Mr Mauro from Switzerland.

25:09.971 --> 25:12.149
Shri Mataji: Who?
Yogi: Mr Mauro from Switzerland.

25:12.350 --> 25:16.056
Shri Mataji: Eh?
Yogis: Switzerland…

