But now only you must choose people
who can come to puja;

27:31.666 --> 27:36.214
everybody can’t bear, you see, this is
too much of vibrations.

27:36.808 --> 27:41.912
But, you see, I know who can come very
easily [of them?],

27:42.113 --> 27:45.029
Very poor things - some of the seekers have
suffered so much

27:45.230 --> 27:51.062
that one puja can settle them down
completely.

27:53.581 --> 27:57.873
It’s all right now, see. Are you all right
now? Person: Yes.

27:58.074 --> 28:02.277
Yogi: He will never again. Shri Mataji: Eh?
Yogi: He will never again.

28:02.478 --> 28:06.399
Shri Mataji: He doesn’t enquire. You know,
you know you have a right.

28:06.600 --> 28:09.453
You are on the right path.]

28:13.055 --> 28:17.349
So we again go back to the same point
is of self-respect.

28:17.994 --> 28:24.932
When you reach that state of love,

28:25.133 --> 28:31.265
respect yourself, then you don’t condemn.

28:32.868 --> 28:36.327
“Because I love Mother, how can I do
such a thing that will bring

28:36.528 --> 28:43.949
bad name to Her? That’s not behooving
the way I should be.

28:44.149 --> 28:49.392
I have to behave in a way that My Mother
likes.”

28:49.942 --> 28:54.265
The whole all question is solved because
you have “Somebody” before you,

28:54.466 --> 28:58.607
and you know what I like and what I
don’t like.

28:59.231 --> 29:05.206
So always you’ll try to do things which
will be pleasing to Me;

29:05.407 --> 29:14.288
but actually it is not such a material
pleasing but is the essence of it,

29:15.577 --> 29:29.493
the essence of pleasing, and that if you
know what will make Me feel pleased…

29:29.694 --> 29:32.218
Actually, I get lost when I think about
My pleasing,

29:32.419 --> 29:36.697
I think, there’s nothing that pleases Me
or displeases Me.

29:36.898 --> 29:42.191
But maybe the Deities part of it, maybe
that part of Me, maybe that,

29:42.392 --> 29:48.006
because They always do things which
will please Me. They know.

29:48.207 --> 29:54.217
So in the same manner, if you can really
work it out,

29:54.799 --> 30:00.440
you’ll get that inner inspiration and
understanding.

30:04.050 --> 30:10.983
The essence of everything, we are
on the principle of it, the Tattwa.

30:11.184 --> 30:17.559
So the essence of everything if you catch…
“What is the essence of this?”

30:19.728 --> 30:23.344
Now put that test to anything.

30:29.520 --> 30:35.162
Just on the essence if you try to live,
the rest is looked after.

30:36.235 --> 30:39.589
So the self-respect, the essence of
self-respect is:

30:39.790 --> 30:43.630
“because I’m a Sahaja Yogi,

30:44.046 --> 30:49.310
because I have got Self Realization and
because I love my Mother”.

30:49.949 --> 30:52.732
This is the essence.

30:55.177 --> 31:06.377
If we can look to the essence of flowers –
why there are so many varieties?

31:08.046 --> 31:12.947
So many varieties of flowers, just see.
Just tremendous. Why?

31:13.148 --> 31:19.940
Because essence of beauty, the aesthetics
of beauty, is variety.

31:21.379 --> 31:26.304
Every leaf, if you take out each leaf

31:26.505 --> 31:33.073
it cannot be matched with anyone in the
whole world, exactly it will not be.

31:34.099 --> 31:39.831
So the essence of aesthetics is variety.

31:40.660 --> 31:44.257
So we have to have Sahaja Yogis
of different varieties,

31:44.458 --> 31:51.362
of different nature, of different humour,
to humour ourselves.

31:51.563 --> 31:55.315
We are not to have everybody just the same.

31:55.516 --> 32:03.292
But in the essence of it, all of them have
to love the Mother.

32:03.743 --> 32:07.915
Then the best of yours that you enjoy
the most,

32:08.116 --> 32:15.590
not the flowers so much, not the nature so
much, nothing more than other Sahaja Yogis.

32:15.791 --> 32:19.866
Once you start enjoying other Sahaja Yogis
and their company,

32:20.067 --> 32:22.876
then you have achieved it.

32:23.910 --> 32:30.384
I mean, imagine enjoying every human being
who is a Sahaja Yogi

32:31.759 --> 32:37.503
and their company, then it’s more than
sufficient. What more do you want?

32:37.704 --> 32:43.270
You don’t enjoy other people, you don’t
enjoy other things so much.

32:43.471 --> 32:48.445
But if you are in a beautiful place and
beautiful circumstances

32:48.646 --> 32:54.483
and you are with other Sahaja Yogis also,
then nothing like this.

32:54.684 --> 33:05.853
It becomes doubly enjoyable, I should say,
and every moment becomes an experience,

33:06.054 --> 33:11.357
every person becomes an experience,
is like a wave of joy.

33:11.558 --> 33:17.847
Every person you meet, every collectivity
you meet, every ashram you go to,

33:18.048 --> 33:23.315
it creates a beautiful wave in your heart
of joy.

33:24.928 --> 33:31.910
My joy is silent, but when I meet somebody,
then it shows itself up.

33:32.111 --> 33:39.535
It comes up like a wave or sometimes
as you see these drops from the ocean

33:39.736 --> 33:44.019
breaking on the shores, beautiful drops.
We call them tushhaar -

33:44.220 --> 33:48.625
in Sanskrit language there’s a beautiful
name for that, tushhaar –

33:49.811 --> 33:58.422
and then the waves go back to your heart.
So beautifully is the relationship

33:58.647 --> 34:04.039
and you just watch it as a witness and
see the joy.

34:05.969 --> 34:13.748
Then everything melts away, all your
knowledge so-called,

34:13.949 --> 34:18.604
all your pains, all your troubles,
all your past,

34:18.805 --> 34:25.688
all your future, but you remain in
the presence, in meditation,

34:25.889 --> 34:30.305
watching all this beautiful happening.

34:30.506 --> 34:38.657
May God all of you understand.
May God in all of you

34:38.858 --> 34:45.177
as Spirit emit that experience
all the time to all of you.

34:45.378 --> 34:48.421
May God bless you.

34:52.896 --> 35:01.902
This is the sari from Greece. Just see
that art of Greece expressed,

35:04.625 --> 35:07.055
beautiful.
Gregoire: It’s like the Aegean sea.

35:07.256 --> 35:12.612
Shri Mataji: Eh?
Gregoire: The water is like the Aegean sea.

35:15.311 --> 35:19.696
Shri Mataji: It’s beautiful. Like in
the sea you have

35:19.897 --> 35:25.976
blue and emerald, both colors, the same
way it is.

35:31.111 --> 35:35.425
So now, only today, because we have come
first time to Turkey,

35:35.626 --> 35:41.476
we’ll just have the establishment of Ganesha
and just wash My feet if possible;

35:41.677 --> 35:45.927
bring some plate, our plate is there.

35:46.128 --> 35:49.596
Gregoire: Shri Mataji, may I just read
a prayer at the beginning of the Puja?

35:49.797 --> 35:52.427
Shri Mataji: All right.

35:56.359 --> 35:59.488
Gregoire: So. Will we take three times
the mantra of Shri Ganesha

35:59.689 --> 36:04.543
and then I will read a prayer for
the beginning of this Puja.

37:20.985 --> 37:28.273
Gregoire: Shri Mataji, we bow before Thee
again and again.

37:29.142 --> 37:35.967
We celebrate this Puja in the old imperial
city called Constantinopolis,

37:36.168 --> 37:43.959
Byzantium and Istanbul, where Islam and
Christianity confronted each other,

37:44.160 --> 37:48.722
on the shores of the Bosphorus, the gateway
between Russia

37:48.923 --> 37:52.916
and the Mediterranean Sea between
north and south,

37:53.117 --> 37:58.786
at the place where Asia and Europe meet
between East and West.

37:58.994 --> 38:02.484
And as these two continents meet here,

38:02.685 --> 38:10.792
may two powerful desires of ours,
Thy children, meet in this Puja.

38:10.993 --> 38:15.304
One desire is for the salvation
of the seekers

38:15.505 --> 38:18.569
and the redemption of this world.

38:18.770 --> 38:24.481
One desire is for Thy welfare, well-being

38:24.682 --> 38:30.254
and good health of Thy earthly Incarnation.

38:36.764 --> 38:39.680
As Asia is bigger than Europe,

38:39.881 --> 38:47.024
so is the second desire of the yogis
much bigger than the first one.

38:48.543 --> 38:54.514
Shri Mataji, we know that Sahaja Yoga
has been born

38:54.715 --> 39:02.027
in the fire of Thy tapasya, is sustained
by the fire of Thy tapasya.

39:02.228 --> 39:08.099
We know that the cool fire of the Kundalini
is powered by the fire of Thy tapasya

39:08.300 --> 39:12.796
and we know, as the whole worlds and
the fourteen universes do,

39:12.997 --> 39:19.357
that Shri Shiva Himself was completely
overcome and conquered by Thy tapasya.

39:19.558 --> 39:22.504
But, Shri Mataji, now it is too much.

39:22.705 --> 39:30.918
The excruciating work and hardship that
Thou take on Thy physical body is inhuman.

39:31.119 --> 39:37.190
And as Thou do all this for us, we pray
now that

39:37.391 --> 39:41.695
as Sahaja Yoga was born in the fire
of Thy penance,

39:41.896 --> 39:47.280
it may now be sprinkled by the cool rain
of Thy satisfaction.

39:47.481 --> 39:52.714
That Sahaja Yoga may now grow through
Thee being prasanya.

39:52.915 --> 39:56.606
Shri Mataji, in the last decade of this
century,

39:56.807 --> 40:02.880
we pray that Sahaja Yoga will develop by
itself in the many countries of this world.

40:03.081 --> 40:12.870
We might for instance organize two or three
important international Sahaja Yoga camps

40:13.071 --> 40:16.623
where people will come from everywhere
as pilgrimage

40:16.824 --> 40:21.602
toward the place where Thou will reside,

40:21.803 --> 40:27.052
so that this punitive travel schedule
should definitely be alleviated;

40:27.253 --> 40:39.111
and we ask this because we are Sahaja Yogis
and because we have our Realization

40:44.548 --> 40:48.318
and because we love our Mother so much.

40:49.559 --> 40:52.864
Shri Mataji: Now his desire power is more,
that’s why he’s crying.

40:53.065 --> 40:56.799
Now let us see that, what our action power
is going to work out.

40:57.000 --> 41:03.010
Put yourself to action power. You see,
the action power when it takes over,

41:03.211 --> 41:07.451
it can be conquered with the desire power.

41:07.810 --> 41:12.593
I also fill so much sometimes with
the desire power

41:12.794 --> 41:19.446
that so much still to be done;

41:19.647 --> 41:25.518
and if you want Me to tell you about it,
you must know

41:25.719 --> 41:33.647
that all these rakshasas who came on this
earth, are known all over the world.

41:33.848 --> 41:36.112
Everyone has heard about TM.

41:36.313 --> 41:43.266
Everybody has heard about all kinds
of hoaxes.Think of it.

41:43.467 --> 41:47.534
People have not even heard about
your Mother.

41:48.257 --> 41:56.894
Now we’ve decided to put our declaration.
We have decided,

41:57.095 --> 42:00.620
but no newspaper will take it.

42:01.082 --> 42:05.151
But if that horrible Rajneesh who has said
that, “I’m a hoax

42:05.360 --> 42:08.002
and I’ve known how to make money

42:08.203 --> 42:12.704
and I’m untruthful and I’m a businessman”,
who has openly said it,

42:12.905 --> 42:17.924
but whatever he says everyday appears
in the newspaper in India.

42:19.426 --> 42:24.470
So when I put Myself onto the other side
of it,

42:24.671 --> 42:30.810
I feel that [a] lot of action still needs
to be done.

42:31.011 --> 42:39.117
Firstly, he has some people who are so
dedicated, surprisingly,

42:39.547 --> 42:44.735
and also they are paid by him because he
has made money, so it’s a vicious circle.

42:44.936 --> 42:47.535
He has made lots of money, he can pay
people,

42:47.736 --> 42:51.648
he can pay newspaper people, he can pay
his disciples so-called,

42:51.849 --> 42:55.761
and make them work for him. So it’s
a paid job.

42:55.962 --> 43:00.553
While Sahaja Yogis have to work on their
own.

43:00.873 --> 43:11.739
So to say that action power of Mine should
stop or should take rest,

43:11.940 --> 43:18.525
it will, when My desire will be fulfilled.

43:19.099 --> 43:26.414
So it has to be established. Still
in Turkey we are afraid a little bit.

43:28.940 --> 43:34.580
Nobody would accept it on the newspaper,
so we have to do something about it,

43:34.781 --> 43:38.785
so that all those who are lost with other
gurus, with other people,

43:38.986 --> 43:45.774
will just jump into it. People don’t even
know our name!

43:49.197 --> 43:53.046
It’s all right, you people have gained
a lot, you have all the enjoyment,

43:53.247 --> 44:00.829
you are all doing everything; but it’s not
yet recorded.

44:02.569 --> 44:05.210
We have to record it,

44:05.411 --> 44:11.317
for that whatever has to be done we cannot
give up, at any cost.

44:17.508 --> 44:20.136
This is the problem.

44:20.337 --> 44:24.523
So at least four years more I have to work
hard, I know that.

44:24.724 --> 44:30.882
As far as My body is concerned, I have
no problem.

44:31.123 --> 44:35.006
I’m eternally fed with energy,

44:35.207 --> 44:39.192
I don’t have problems, you don’t worry
about Me.

44:39.393 --> 44:44.397
I look like an ordinary human being,
I’m not.

44:49.007 --> 44:55.383
So don’t you worry. Be satisfied.

44:55.584 --> 44:59.536
I’m not in any way harmed, no one can
harm Me,

44:59.737 --> 45:03.903
no one can kill Me, nothing.

45:04.381 --> 45:08.955
But we have to establish, that’s important.

45:11.066 --> 45:21.031
Even a very ordinary person from India

45:21.249 --> 45:24.509
becomes well-known on the spiritual field,
just imagine,

45:24.710 --> 45:32.456
who has done no work, somebody hanging
in the air.

45:42.176 --> 45:53.494
So like I would say also that we have
to make sacrifices.

45:53.939 --> 46:00.984
As far as your feeling are concerned about
Me, that you don’t have to worry,

46:01.185 --> 46:03.695
you are all looking after Me very well.

46:03.896 --> 46:11.511
I’m overfed, not with food only but with
love and affection.

46:11.712 --> 46:15.913
But we have to still do very much,
that would do.

46:16.372 --> 46:20.270
So don’t you worry about Me, I’m perfectly
all right.

46:20.479 --> 46:26.956
Do I look tired to you?
Gregoire: No, Shri Mataji, not now.

46:32.381 --> 46:37.993
Yogi: Gregoire, Gregoire.
Shri Mataji: This is not recorded, is it?

46:38.919 --> 46:44.903
Yogi: It is on there, Shri Mataji.
Shri Mataji: All right, camera is this on.

46:47.970 --> 46:56.111
[Hindi] Now, today [Hindi].

46:59.338 --> 47:04.467
Now today, you see, according to Hersh
is that in India,

47:04.668 --> 47:07.430
they don’t wash My hands but wash My feet.

47:07.631 --> 47:14.435
Yogi: We deserve to worship Your feet,
they do so much work, Shri Mataji…

47:14.910 --> 47:17.466
Shri Mataji: No, but moreover the vibrations
are much more there,

47:17.667 --> 47:19.783
I don’t know.
Yogi: Yes.

47:20.007 --> 47:23.306
Shri Mataji: Is said that [Sanskrit words],

47:23.507 --> 47:29.852
“from the Feet of such [a] person flows
the river Ganges”, you see,

47:30.053 --> 47:36.750
or the river of the Gods, you see.
So the Feet have that speciality.

47:36.927 --> 47:40.531
And imagine, the other day we did not do
this washing,

47:40.732 --> 47:44.425
so Hersh told Me that, “Let us do the Feet
washing”.

47:44.626 --> 47:48.966
And we did it in this pot which is made
of copper.

47:49.167 --> 47:52.651
And there was also some copper into it.

47:52.852 --> 47:57.592
The whole night it was kept with the copper,
and it gets poisonous.

47:57.793 --> 48:05.402
But nobody felt the poison. On the contrary,
vibrations improved.

48:08.569 --> 48:13.050
So the poison was neutralized.
Just like when Shiva

48:13.259 --> 48:16.158
drank all the poison and nothing happened,
in the same way.

48:16.359 --> 48:18.189
[Indian yogi comments:“We had once prepared
in Madras,

48:18.390 --> 48:25.613
I mean, in three hours it just –
(indistinct) – then Mother repeated this” -

48:25.921 --> 48:28.453
“Mother repeated”. (unclear)]

