Sheersha. Atharva Sheersha.

48:45.510 --> 48:49.714
If the people – if you try to remember
things by heart,

48:49.915 --> 48:55.852
even some songs will be good idea, so that
you needn’t have books.

48:57.707 --> 49:02.231
